          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "PHDIF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " As  in  the  residual  nucleus B-11 the first",
                " excited state is located at  energy  2.12  MeV,  the",
                " cross   section   of  (g,p0)  reaction  was  deduced",
                " straightforwardly  from  the  measured   photoproton",
                " spectra,  taken  at  three  bremsstrahlung end-point",
                " energies 25,  27, and 29 MeV simultaneously at seven",
                " angles varying between 37 and 143 degrees.",
                "Then  the  spectra   were   used   to    obtain   the",
                " integrated-over-angles cross    section   by   using",
                " Shiff's bremsstrahlung spectrum expression."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The statistical errors."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The systematic error was estimated to be about",
                " of 12%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The absolute  differential  cross  sections  for  the",
                " reaction  C-12(g,p0)B-11  were  measured  at   seven",
                " angles  in  the energy region between 21 and 29 MeV.",
                " using a standard legendre polynomial expansion,  the",
                " total   integrated-over-angles  absolute  C-12(g,p0)",
                " cross section was derived."
              ]
            }
          ],
